Nearby, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, while volunteers gather leftover brochures and stack collapsed booths in a designated area. Friends decompress at the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly to their applications, and some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the scene, and a welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcast over the PA system.

Nearby, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops while camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the scene. Volunteers gather leftover brochures and stack collapsed booths in a designated area. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, and a welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcast over the PA system. As the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names.

Nearby, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, while volunteers gather leftover brochures and stack collapsed booths in a designated area. Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the event, and some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcast over the PA system, and as the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names.
